loafer is a 1996 indian bollywood film directed by david dhawan and produced by surinder kapoor and sarang sonalkar . it stars anil kapoor and juhi chawla in pivotal roles . the film was a remake of the superhit telugu film titled assembly rowdy ( 1991 ) starring divya bharti and mohan babu which itself was a remake of 1990 in tamil film velai kidaichuduchu .